channel.title: Dylan's copy
channel.description:
Dylan said he was going to make that sword a contest so I thought I should try and see how I do. Rate, Hate, Masterbate. There will be NO releasing because this is a copy of dylan's work. If dylan thinks I am gay for doing this I will remove. ;D Didn't add wings because I got bored of model. May finish at later date. Kind of busy. Some views: [URL=http://img42.imageshack.us/my.php?image=dylanscopy.jpg][IMG]http://img42.imageshack.us/img42/7219/dylanscopy.th.jpg[/img][/URL]
[URL=http://img4.imageshack.us/my.php?image=dylanscopy1.jpg][IMG]http://img4.imageshack.us/img4/8064/dylanscopy1.th.jpg[/img][/URL]
[URL=http://img820.imageshack.us/my.php?image=dylanscopy2.jpg][IMG]http://img820.imageshack.us/img820/4959/dylanscopy2.th.jpg[/img][/URL]
[URL=http://img13.imageshack.us/my.php?image=wireframe1.jpg][IMG]http://img13.imageshack.us/img13/918/wireframe1.th.jpg[/img][/URL]
And Dylan didn't lie. Easily made under polygon limits. And like I said, if this was a gay idea, I'll remove. Don't flame me to hard. Completion time: 10 hours approx. Made in Metasequioa. Only good thing imo about blender is the textures...
